HBASE_REMOTE_TESTING

public static final Constants.Term HBASE_REMOTE_TESTING
Use the properties defined for HBase to connect to a remote HBase instance. Important: for local development, set the variable to false.

HBASE_PROPERTIES

public static final Constants.Term HBASE_PROPERTIES
Properties used when connecting to a remote instance of HBase. Use SQWDEV to configure HBase to use the SeqWare development cluster, use HBOOT to configure HBase to use OICR's HBase cluster, use LOCAL to configure HBase for use on a local machine.
